dc_description_s: This data layer represents trails for Vilas County, Wisconsin in 2022. [A trail or path used for walking, cycling, hiking or other form of non-vehicular transportation. In some cases, other forms of motorized transportation may be permitted on a regular or seasonal basis.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: https://data-vilas.opendata.arcgis.com/
